        "thisType": "Psychotherapy",
        "title": "Psychotherapy Note",
        "text": "Dream Imagery--journey to an unknown destination with a group of familiar and unfamiliar people, mountains, sunflowers, a dance party. He expressed feeling guilty over past arguments with his sister and being dismissive of his when they were children. Stirred feelings in me of loss of my mother and my own adjustment issues and feelings of guilt.",
        "formattedText": "<p>Dream Imagery–journey to an unknown destination with a group of familiar and unfamiliar people, mountains, sunflowers, a dance party. He expressed feeling guilty over past arguments with his sister and being dismissive of his when they were children. Stirred feelings in me of loss of my mother and my own adjustment issues and feelings of guilt.</p>\n",
